			<abstract>
				<p>Testimony of Suwałki resident and homeowner Pese R. on the transfer of power from the Soviets to the Germans, the subsequent German
					occupation of Suwałki, and incipient persecution of Jews. She retells her flight from Suwałki with her children being stranded in
					“no man's land” at the Lithuanian border for some time, threatened to be deported to the “Lublin Reservation” but finally making
					it over the border to Lithuania.</p>
			</abstract>
		</profileDesc>
